title: Freezer for ice-cream US-SD-408Y
short_description: With an internal capacity of 408 liters, this US-SD-408Y freezer can cool from 0°C to -18°C. Such freezers can store not only ice cream, but also semi-finished products and many similar things. The refrigerator is 1239 mm long, 660 mm wide and 845 mm high.

Bu kabi morozilniklar nafaqat muzqaymoqlarni, balki yarimtayyor mahsulotlar va shunga o'xshash ko'plab narsalarni o'zida saqlay oladi. Muzlatgich uzunligi 1239 mm, kengligi 660 mm va balandligi 845 mm ni tashkil etadi.
